snippet.title: REBOUND | A Road Trip Turns Into a Nightmare | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A woman leaves everything behind to start over.
The road ahead leads somewhere far more dangerous.

After a painful betrayal, Claire leaves Los Angeles and begins a long drive back to her hometown of Chicago, hoping distance will help her heal. But as the miles pass, her journey takes a disturbing turn. What begins as an escape soon becomes a confrontation with a reality far darker than the one she tried to leave behind.

Director: Megan Freels Johnston
Cast: Ashley James, Mark Meir, Wes O’Lee.
